task.summary: Default task

First iteration of FloatingInfo export.
Added shapeout by default in XML export.
Included new post-processing tools in plugin setup window and data structure. May not be compatible with previous versions.
Added ComputeForces post processing tool
Implemented MeasureTool post processing tool

Cosmetic changes
Changes _Out folder suffix with _out (capitalization). Changes Save & Run GenCase dialog a bit.
Adds FlowTool to Case Summary

Various fixes and additions
Fixes typos in case summary. Adds new type of info dialog for post-processing. Disables batch script generation. Changes texts on some components.

Filters move and rotate commands on the XML
They no longer appear if the values don't make any difference.
Now STL files are referenced with relative paths
Changes AWAS config labels to show units
Adds Slice or Surface selector to IsoSurface post-processing tool
Adds mk/id/position selector to ComputeForces export
Changes open with paraview button from save menu

Makes details dialog on GenCase saving a popup.
Hacked through the garbage collector to do it, so the menu appears when the dialog is not modal, avoiding using exec_()
Fixes FlowTool point order and changes the reference image

Removes space restrictions on save path
DualSPHysics now supports paths with spaces on it, so there's no need to keep DesignSPHysics forcing the users to save in a folder which path contains no spaces.
Fixes #18

Implements FlowTool executable check
Now when the FlowTool executable is missing or incorrect the application will try to load one from the config file and warn the user.
Fixes xml dump for fillboxes and corrects some strings
Implements draft of MultiLayered Pistons and Relaxation Zones
Added Milti-Layer Pistons 2D
Disbled damping overlimit visualization temporarily until it's fixed
Adds particle count to Case Summary

Adds option to open IsoSurface export with Paraview
Also, removes type selection from IsoSurface as it can only export fluids, so it does not need it.
Now opening with Paraview in PartVTK is only enabled if VTK is selected
Fixes an error where FloatingInfo would put -onlyprocess instead of -onlymk
Removes size constraints in multiple windows
Changes Motion Configuration window to have a QSplitter instead of fixed components.
Changes some messages and names on the interface
Now when DesignSPHysics autofills the executable paths, it gets saved to the disk
Now linear and rotational motions from file uses relative paths.
Removes matrixreset from fillboxes
Changes version
Implemented Damping with overlimit
Fixes XML end tags on Acceleration Inputs
Implemented Uniform Velocity Relaxation Zone
Fixes rotation from a file (Movement) being detected as wave generator
Fixes some errors with movements
Implemented basic functionality for external waves (SWASH)
Relaxation Zone with external data now copies the velocity files to the out folder and changes its path to a relative one.
Commenting and refactor pass.
Adds DualSPHysics executables in a new directory

Changed how different needed files for the cases are copied
Changing the name of the project would make a reference error due to relative paths. To solve this the files needed to movements, accinputs, etc. are now copied both to the case root and the out folder. If the out folder gets removed of its name changes, the files on the project root will be copied instead of having to search for the file full path again.
Prevents movements from exporting into the XML if they don't exist
Did some code cleaning and refactoring

Adds text constants for help messages
Also adds a custom QLabel implementation with hover event.
Changes some bits like minimum required version and some details in the README.md file.
Refactorizes Constant Definition Dialog to be a new class

Adds a custom QLineEdit implementation with focus event
Adds more text constants for help messages

Refactorizes Execution Parameters Dialog to be a new class
Did code cleaning.

Added a warning window about save case in "Run GenCase"
Added "run_gencase.png" to images folder
